
This patch is contributed by Andy Gay <andy@andynet.net>

See:  http://bugs.xelerance.com/view.php?id=538

This issue is fixed in openswan 3.x differently, using the "deflate"
keyword as part of the esp= proposal, which will be backported to 2.5,
but not to 2.4. Since we do not have the resources right now to fully
test the impact of this patch, we're supplying it as a contrib patch.

Paul
